      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1778651027128,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Domain Entities (json)\nE.g: transactions, budgets, goals\n(personal finance) ",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "8VfKnkMH3IKbXcH0PgGky",
      "originalText": "Domain Entities (json)\nE.g: transactions, budgets, goals (personal finance) ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yF-ptwKo1CDIS-Wqlz5O8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1122.5610082129774,
      "y": 1372.120944001792,
      "width": 1764.336330676428,
      "height": 368.647339413641,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b05",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1200035777,
      "version": 1349,
      "versionNonce": 1389063040,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777273306829,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Each incoming data source has to be processed differently\n- Each memory system extracts relevant information from each of the\ndata source and stores it in a format that it (the memory system)\nunderstands and supports fuzzy search\n- Evaluation and feedback play an important role to understand what\nmemories extracted were useful vs what were not",
      "fontSize": 49.15297858848547,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Each incoming data source has to be processed differently\n- Each memory system extracts relevant information from each of the data source and stores it in a format that it (the memory system) understands and supports fuzzy search\n- Evaluation and feedback play an important role to understand what memories extracted were useful vs what were not",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p1miZO5xpUawwVRK-EebX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2124.9793910810345,
      "y": 1411.3512525217384,
      "width": 1229.3193229954336,
      "height": 329.97963191666156,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b07",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1229901505,
      "version": 892,
      "versionNonce": 1644903552,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777273368084,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Retrieval is a fuzzy search problem\n- Context Construction is a use-case (domain) problem\n- It requires understanding of the use-case (domain),\nthe problem and \"memory\" of what has worked in the\npast. \n- Evaluation and feedback play an important role",
      "fontSize": 43.997284255554874,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Retrieval is a fuzzy search problem\n- Context Construction is a use-case (domain) problem\n- It requires understanding of the use-case (domain), the problem and \"memory\" of what has worked in the past. \n- Evaluation and feedback play an important role",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Z6lxCn8oVAN8SmN-WEyHy",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1181.4880652463958,
